ATTACK - Start combat
=====================

Usage: attack <target>

Initiates combat with a monster or player in the same room.

Examples:
  attack rat
  attack orc
  attack wolf

Combat proceeds automatically in rounds every 2 seconds. You will continue
fighting until one of you dies or you flee by moving to another room.

Notes:
  - Make sure you have good equipment before fighting
  - Check your HP during combat with the 'hp' command
  - Some monsters are aggressive and will attack you first!
  - You can flee by moving to an exit

See also: help combat, help hp, help death
